org.apache.beam.sdk.metrics

Class MetricName

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.beam.sdk.metrics.MetricName
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    @Experimental(value=METRICS)
public abstract class MetricName
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The name of a metric consists of a namespace() and a name(). The namespace() allows grouping related metrics together and also prevents collisions between multiple metrics with the same name.
